description._content: Edinburgh city in the blurred background

Managed to find some snow close by Edinburgh last weekend as didn't have time to go further afield. 

This is on the Old Kirk Road path between Scald Law and Carnethy Hill. This is looking towards Black Hill.

The light stayed for about half and hour then went so was lucky to catch this.
